The incident happened along the border of Molo and Elburgon.
Mr Munari urged residents to take care of their children especially during this period of the Covid-19 pandemic and the December festive season.
Police have launched investigations into the ncident.
The bodies were moved to Molo Sub-County Hospital mortuary.

